## Judgement Analysis System

An AI-powered Legal Intelligence Platform designed to automate the analysis of judicial documents using Machine Learning, NLP, and Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

The system enables fast, structured, and intelligent understanding of complex legal judgments through advanced AI pipelines.

## Key Features

1.User Authentication (Login / Register / Secure Sessions)
2.PDF Judgment Processing with automated text extraction
3.Legal Domain Classification using ML models
4.AI-powered Case Summarization using LLMs
5.Semantic Search powered by FAISS vector database
6.Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) for contextual insights
7.User Notes & Annotations System
8.Bookmarking & Case Management
9.Interactive Dashboard with Insights
10.Similar Case Retrieval System
11.System Architecture

The system follows an end-to-end AI pipeline:

Text Extraction → PDF parsing using pdfplumber
Preprocessing & Chunking → Clean and split large documents
Embedding Generation → Sentence Transformers (LegalBERT)
Domain Classification → ML model (XGBoost)
Vector Search → FAISS for similarity retrieval
RAG Pipeline → Context-aware retrieval
LLM Processing → LLaMA 3.3 via Groq API for insights

